/* welcome */
Welcome to FirstVu ticket ordering system!

/* create */
enter username to create
enter account type
enter user account balance
create successful

/* addcredit */
enter username          //Admin only
enter credit amount
new balance: $--
credit added

/* sell */
enter event title
enter sale price
enter number of tickets
tickets added

/* buy */
enter event title
enter number of tickets
enter username of seller
cost per ticket: $--
total cost: $--
current balance: $--
confirm purchase: yes or no
new balance: $--
purchase successful

/* refund */
enter buyer's username
enter seller's username
enter amount to transfer
refund successful

/* delete */
enter username
delete successful

/* logout */
logout successful

/* login */
enter username
login successful

/* end */
Goodbye!


