error: invalid parameters
error: user not authorized to sell
error: event already exists
error: invalid event price								//price over 999.99 or less than 0
error: event title must be a maximum of 25 characters
error: invalid ticket number							//over 100 or less than 1
error: tickets unavailable

/* buy */
error: user not authorized to buy
error: insufficient funds
error: a maximum of 4 tickets can be purchased
error: not enough tickets remaining
error: invalid seller name
error: invalid event
error: invalid ticket number

/* refund */
error: only administrators can make refunds
error: username does not exist
error: total balance cannot be greater than $999 999
error: no transaction found
